window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What kind of superpowered supervillain robs a bank?</b></p> <p>After technically being dead for twenty-six years, Marcus might be an old dog with some old-school ideas, but he's got some new tricks up his sleeve. Now that he's learned all about the modern world and his new abilities, he's ready to make his move. Thanks to the women he lured to the dark side, he's going to start things off with a bang. That's why he's going to rob a bank. He's ready to put Arch City on notice. There is a new player in town and it's time he got the respect he deserved.</p> <p>Unbeknownst to Marcus, he is being hunted by both sides of the law. The most powerful superhero in the world wants him brought in because of the danger he might become, while a ruthless, rival supervillain wants him captured and brought to heel. If Marcus wants to take his rightful place at the top of the city's pecking order, he's going to need a lot more than a few million dollars. He might need an extra set of hands. It's a good thing he already has some willing volunteers.</p> <p>If at first you don't succeed, try, try again. This time, failure is not an option.</p> <p><i>Narrated in duet style.</i></p>"; 
